Create a modern crypto trading dashboard with real-time price charts, portfolio management, and trading interface. The application should include:

- Real-time cryptocurrency price tracking
- Interactive charts and graphs
- Portfolio overview with profit/loss tracking
- Trading interface with buy/sell functionality
- Market news and updates
- Responsive design for mobile and desktop
- Dark theme with modern UI components

Use Vite, React, TypeScript, and shadcn/ui components for a professional trading platform experience. 